Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而他们显然因为某种理由在隐瞒真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they clearly have a reason for suppressing the truth."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's one interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,另一种解释是泰勒·戴维斯有心理疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The other is that Tyler Davis had a mental-health crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这两种解释中  只有一种解释有事实支撑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And only one of those interpretations has the facts to support it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他说过还有上千个像他一样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"He spoke of thousands more like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We should be --"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该印出化装舞会上真正发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"We should be printing what really happened at the masquerade ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但你只想改述弥尔顿总管在通稿中的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But, instead, you want to paraphrase what Governor Milton said in her press release."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不  康妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你去改述弥尔顿总管在通稿中的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want you to paraphrase Governor Milton's press release
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下次  我就不用亲自出马了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so that the next time, I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,既然没人见过她  没人和她说过话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if no one's seen her and no one's talked to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那她是怎么请假的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how can she have called in sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没说她请假了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never said she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道  我来顶班是因为她没现身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All I know is, I was told to be here because she didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定要这样做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人劫持过人质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The guy took a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他当时担心自己的安危\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was afraid for his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也担心过自己的安危\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been afraid for my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我从没有劫持过无辜人质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've never taken an innocent hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想知道他认为帕梅拉做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just want to know what he thinks Pamela did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你之所以想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The only reason you want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因为他们想隐瞒这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is because they're trying to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是私人病房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a private room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒·戴维斯  他有律师吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Tyler Davis -- does he have a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他被指控了什么罪名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are the charges against him?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦军\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is C.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被要求检查你的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've been asked to perform a wellness check.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,请开门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她不在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那我想立刻作供\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I'd like to make a statement immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,趁我记忆犹新时  详述她最后的行踪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}recount the details of her last-knowns on the record now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,以供记录在案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}while this is still fresh in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好  来站里一趟  我帮你填文件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sure. Come down to the station. I'll help you fill out the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你常这样出行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How often do you take trips like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没我希望的那么频繁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not as often as I'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这听起来可能很疯狂  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This probably sounds crazy, but
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉比起在城市里  我在外面感觉更好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I feel like I'm better out here than I am in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来一点不疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It doesn't sound crazy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的很多人也有同感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A lot of my people feel that way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你仍然分你们和我们啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You still see this as your people and my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你看这个地方是如何运作的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want you to see how this place works,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我希望你成为它的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because I want you to be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,总的来说  我混得还不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've done fairly well, all things considered,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不是一开始就处在顶端\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but let's just say I didn't start out on the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在算处在顶端吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that where you are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,勉强算吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,弥尔顿总管管理这座城市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Governor Milton runs the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道它是如何运作的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I know how it runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你是从底层打拼上来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because you started out at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前  我向弥尔顿家族证明了我的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I proved myself to the Milton family a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你跟正确的人打交道  卡萝尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you're in with the right people, Carol,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你的前途不可限量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the sky's the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,向上爬时你会学到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And one of the things you learn as you're climbing your way up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,任何组织内都有两种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is that there are two types of people in any organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一种是佣兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On the one hand, you've got the mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拿钱干活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're in it for the money
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,靠地位来满足自己的某种欲望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and whatever psychological itch their position allows them to scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,另一种是爱国者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And on the other, you have the patriots,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,忠诚信徒  想做好事的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the true believers, the ones who want to do good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,至于做的是不是好事也许有待商榷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And whether they are or not might be up to debate,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们加入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but in their hearts, they're there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为他们真心相信组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because they believe in the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我来就是为了这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that why I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,把我改造成忠诚信徒吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want to make a true believer out of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我读过你的档案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I read your file.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你来是因为你够聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're here because you're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你能帮我应付这个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think you'll be able to help me deal with this asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,至于你怎么想  那取决于你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What you get out of it is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:12:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,毒贩还是走私贩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Drug dealers or smugglers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是走私贩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're smugglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但这与你想的不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方严格来说不属于联邦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This place is not exactly a part of the Commonwealth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们需要他们  他们需要我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but they need us, and we need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们用罂粟为医院制作鸦片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We use the poppies to make opium for the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果用完了  那里的情况会变得很糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Things will start looking pretty bleak there if we run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我负责确保这不会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I make sure that doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但有时候  我得和莫托这样的人打交道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But, sometimes, that means dealing with guys like Moto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过会发生这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told you what was gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而我说过你要处理好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I asked you to manage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我说服他们加工了最后一批货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I talked them into processing this last batch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Best I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过他们会扣下收成的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told you they're gonna hold the harvest hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要求加薪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They want a raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不加  他们发誓让收成烂在地里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They swear they'll let it rot without one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来看看怎么办吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, let's see what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是《论坛报》的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're with the Tribune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,去2号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're in number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,珍知道我对警察军事化怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以派我来写随队宣传文章
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想惹她生气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你应该考虑一下按她的要求办事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,最近没见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I haven't seen you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在固定范围内我还算正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm functioning within to-be-expected parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我看出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, no, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以能让我进去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, so can you let me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我带了千层面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I brought lasagna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,盘子是空的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is an empty dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我没做千层面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't make lasagna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一般带食物别人都会让你进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}People just always have to let you in if you're carrying food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦军放弃了搜索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the C.A. Gave up the search,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定亲自调查史蒂芬妮的失踪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I decided to investigate Stephanie's disappearance myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,实话说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Truth be told,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,随着时间流逝  线索无迹可寻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as the hours tick by with nary a bread crumb to be found,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我被绝望吞噬了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I let my despair get the best of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,直到一次偶遇让我发现了端倪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is, until a chance encounter put me on the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir. Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我要和你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  我要谈谈...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please, I need to talk --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,雷辛街1634号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}1634 Racine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一号住宅区的一座公寓楼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's an apartment building in Residential One.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,三天前  你被看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three days ago, you were seen --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在晚上七点下了楼梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at 7:00 in the P.M., you were seen coming down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不记得了  -等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I don't remember this. - Uh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, sir, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:16:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一位至亲失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone near and dear to me has gone missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你也许看到了能帮我找到她的线索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you may have seen something that might help me find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里来着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一号住宅区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Residential One.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,三天前  大概晚上七点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three days ago, at approximately 7:00 in the P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一号住宅区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At Residential One.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在想起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我被叫去通水槽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got called in to fix a clogged sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里看到她了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What -- Do -- Do you remember seeing her there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里看到她了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you remember seeing her there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,或者当晚在附近有没有看到什么可疑情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or anything suspicious in or around the premises that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,够了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我真心抱歉打扰了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I sincerely apologize for having troubled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哪天有空我们可以谈谈...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there's a better time in which we could talk --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不必说  我对他的说法相当怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Needless to say, I greeted his story with a great deal of skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,当晚街头没有城市服务车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There were no city service carts on the street that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他也没有穿着明显制服或携带任何工具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}nor was he wearing any sort of identifying uniform or carrying any tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在她失踪当晚  唯一一个在场的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I found it very peculiar that the one person I knew was there
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有如此经不起推敲的托辞  令我非常奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the night she disappeared happened to have such a flimsy alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我开始跟踪他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I started following him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这个管道工是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, like, what's this plumber's deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,首先\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To start with,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫罗曼·卡尔霍恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}his name is Roman Calhoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定不是个管道工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And he is most definitely not a plumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他通常在晚上办事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He mostly conducts his business at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他的行动基地是仓库区的一座大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His base of operations is a building in the warehouse district,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这家公司自称是管道服务承包商\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which purports to be a purveyor of plumbing services
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在表面上看是合法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and which, on the surface, appears to be legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  他们从没有收到过任何邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, they never receive any mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,非营业时间里面亮着灯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's lights on at odd hours, when they're ostensibly closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还有人经常进出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And while people go in and out with a fair degree of regularity,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,通常都是同样的四个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's usually just the same four people over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们独自抵达  然后很快离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They usually arrive alone and depart shortly thereafter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,经常两人一组会面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and frequently meeting in groups of two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一次全员到齐  并有第五人到场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And on the one occasion they were all together, they were also met by a fifth,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他就是老大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who I also believe to be the head honcho,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他是政府内流氓势力的幕后黑手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the mastermind of some sort of rogue element
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芬妮不知为何得罪了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}within the government that Stephanie somehow ran afoul of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,流氓势力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rogue element?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为是政府的人绑架了她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like, you think she was kidnapped by the government or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在我开始搜索不久之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shortly after I began my search,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我后来所知道的二号同谋者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the man who later became known to me as Co-Conspirator Number Two,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是"圆帽男"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a.K.A. "Beanie Hat Man,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来到了史蒂芬妮的公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}showed up to Stephanie's apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,带着一队搬家工  带走了她的所有东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with a team of movers, collected all her belongings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,将之运去了未知地点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and took them to an unknown location.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在同一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then, that same day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芬妮在联合车站的档案中出现了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this was found in Stephanie's file at Union Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这是史蒂芬妮在失踪当天签的工作调动申请\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a work-transfer request signed by Stephanie on the day of her disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那天在无线电室给她顶班的男子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The man who filled in for her at the radio room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,说她并没有提前申请过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that day told me she gave no notice whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没有权力机构的直接干涉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Such orders could not be falsified or fabricated
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这种调令是不可能被篡改或伪造的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}without direct influence from within the halls of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道他们要找她算账\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She knew they were coming for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在她逃跑以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When she eluded them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们申请了假工作调动来掩盖她的失踪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they filed that false work transfer to cover up her disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为了取回她搜集的证据  他们运走了她的所有东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They took all her belongings to recover any evidence she may have gathered,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在修补漏洞的最后一步只剩抹消她了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and now silencing her is the last step in repairing that leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I'm right,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她唯一的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}her only hope
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我赶在他们找到她之前曝光他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is for me to expose them before they find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,今年渔获如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good hatches this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,捕了足够的鱼  我现在钓鱼只是为了娱乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We catch enough that I can actually just do it for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你的爱好也是一项末日技能真好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's nice when your hobby is also an apocalypse skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Amen to that.
