Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.71,0:39:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道的关于我们社区的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}everything you wanted to know about our communities.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.21,0:39:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.21,0:40:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她引我去了火车场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She led me to the train yard,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.62,0:40:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在那里被你抓住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where we were captured by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.75,0:40:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我好欺负\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You thought I wa-- you thought I was an easy mark,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.04,0:40:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,最信任警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the most trusting of the police, so you --
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.21,0:40:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你把我的朋友们一个个拆散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you split off my friends one at a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.12,0:40:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,以为我的防线会崩溃  但我没崩溃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}thinking I'd break, but I didn't break.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.25,0:40:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她引我去了无线电室  我们再次被抓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then she led me to the -- the radio room, where we were captured again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.41,0:40:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这次你倒是赚翻了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, and you certainly got your money's worth there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.29,0:40:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我竟然上了两次当\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I actually fell for that one twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.91,0:40:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她说我可以信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's the one that told me I can trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.21,0:40:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而我信任了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.58,0:40:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她甚至读了我的小说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She even read my book
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.54,0:40:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,以获取任何有用的自传式信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so that she could get any helpful autobiographical information
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.37,0:40:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来满足你的需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that might serve your needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.66,0:40:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你得到了想要的一切  怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But now that you've gotten everything you wanted, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.46,0:40:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,骗局没必要再继续了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No need to continue the ruse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.08,0:40:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.08,0:41:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但你没料到这个反转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you didn't see this twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.79,0:41:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会让所有人都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am gonna make absolutely certain that everybody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.79,0:41:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你的真面目是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}exactly who and what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.08,0:41:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.50,0:41:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,具体来说  是什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And who or what is that, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.83,0:41:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,恶人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The villain?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.54,0:41:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The boogeyman?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.66,0:41:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还是你们遇见的最大贵人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or the best goddamn thing that ever happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.96,0:41:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对  尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're right, Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.54,0:41:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是骗了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.75,0:41:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你和你朋友们为了进这里  满口扯谎一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just like you and your friends lied through your teeth to get inside these walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.91,0:41:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.41,0:41:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但谁会分那么清呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But who's keeping score, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.04,0:41:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让你们来这里  我的确做了一些事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, I did what I had to do to get you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.50,0:41:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗  你们应该为此感谢我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you know what? You should be thanking me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.50,0:41:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你们蠢到不知道天上掉了馅饼可不是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not my fault you people are too stupid to know a good thing when it landed in your laps.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.37,0:42:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你就直接承认了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're just -- you're just admitting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.00,0:42:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱上了她  而我所知的她的一切都是假象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I fell in love, and everything I know about her is a fiction!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.46,0:42:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当你动了真情时  我们试过让你面对现实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, we tried to rip the Band-Aid off when we saw it was getting serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.58,0:42:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我用尽办法阻止你寻找她  但你就是不停手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I did everything I could to get you to stop looking for her, but you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.41,0:42:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,结果闹成了这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.54,0:42:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,至少你现在能停手了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least you can stop now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.41,0:42:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当时你们的情况不会好转  尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't gonna get better for your people, Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.21,0:42:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们将会饿死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They were about to starve.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.25,0:42:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你们来了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now you're here
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.33,0:42:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的社区得到了修缮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and your community is getting fixed
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.29,0:42:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们得到了一切  从音乐会到癌症手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you've got everything, from concerts to cancer surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.71,0:42:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们对你们的唯一要求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And literally the only thing we've ever asked of you all in return
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.04,0:42:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是成为对这里有贡献的成员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is to be productive members of society here
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.62,0:42:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你们自愿留下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for as long as you choose to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.37,0:42:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  随心所欲地告诉他们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, tell them whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.00,0:42:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你为了出狱签的那份声明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The statement you signed to get out of jail
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.29,0:43:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,上面写着你因神经焦虑导致了偏执\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}says you were suffering from paranoia as a result of nervous strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.37,0:43:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.04,0:43:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你  尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, look at you, Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.71,0:43:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这显然对你打击很大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This has obviously taken a toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.50,0:43:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你心碎了我遗憾吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Am I sorry your heart got broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.41,0:43:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.79,0:43:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你的朋友们听说了一定也很难过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I'm sure your friends will be very sad to hear about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.21,0:43:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但权衡一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But in the balance of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.00,0:43:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我仍觉得这个结果对大家都好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I still think it worked out in everyone's favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.41,0:43:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们应该也会这样想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they probably would, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.91,0:43:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.79,0:43:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说句\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.75,0:43:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芬妮的真名是席拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stephanie's real name is Shira.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.37,0:43:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她讨厌铁娘子乐队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And she hates Iron Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.66,0:44:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但她真的很喜欢你的小说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But she genuinely enjoyed your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.96,0:44:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该继续写下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You should stick with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.04,0:45:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Eugene?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.87,0:45:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.54,0:45:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金  我要和你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Eugene, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.62,0:45:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,土豆虫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tater Bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.37,0:45:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝象甲呼叫土豆虫  请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Blue Weevil to Tater Bug. Please come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.00,0:45:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.21,0:45:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.54,0:45:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在无线电里和你通话的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm the one you were talking to on the radio.
